  "explanation": "<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p>Pitanja u vremenu <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Simple Past</span> koriste <span class=\"highlighted-text\">did</span> + subjekat + osnovni glagol. Primer:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">What did Sophie say?</span> – <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Did</span> pokazuje da je prošlo vreme, i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">say</span> je glagol osnove.</p>\n<p>Naspravno tome, pozitivna forma direktno koristi glagol prošlog vremena. Na primer:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Sophie said that the movie was great.</span> – Prethodna forma za <span class=\"highlighted-text\">say</span> je <span class=\"highlighted-text\">said</span>.</p>\n</section>",
